This blade possesses an unearthly splendor, and it is likely that Sune, the goddess of beauty and passion, had a hand in its creation. The effect it has on the wielder is immediate, and more than once in its history has this sword has been the secret behind a lackluster soldier's sudden elevation at court. This blade has been enhanced by Ruad to be a more effective weapon yes, but it's most unique feature is its stunning beauty. Long after it leaves the hands of its current user, it will be a cherished item for Court and Ceremony. Many have said it's appearance is unnaturally beautiful and possible only through magical means. Truly splendid regardless of how it was made, one almost wonders how such great beauty can bring such great death as well.

